<paragraph id="6D0836D113005C5EFF2DFA02CF54F9AC" blockId="4.[166,1224,1343,1562]" pageId="4" pageNumber="457">
Bionomics. Most material collected in Ukrainian is from 
<collectingRegion id="AF73F83313005C5EFC66FA02C950FA0C" box="[912,1093,1439,1465]" country="Ukraine" name="Zakarpattya" pageId="4" pageNumber="457">Transcarpathia</collectingRegion>
, where this species in 2017 was numerous and common. This contrasts collection events at the same time in 2018 and 2019, where it was not seen to be numerous. Ukrainian collected material dates from 7 May to 26 September.
</paragraph>
